### POST request to create food allergy
POST http://localhost:4000/patients/{{patient_id}}/allergies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "{{patient_id}}",
  "allergen": "Peanuts",
  "allergyType": "FOOD",
  "severity": "LIFE_THREATENING",
  "reaction": "Anaphylaxis, severe swelling, respiratory distress",
  "notes": "Diagnosed in childhood. Patient must avoid all peanut products and foods processed in facilities with peanuts. EpiPen prescribed.",
  "isActive": true
}

